data.description: Great updated home with lots of natural light.  Home includes a built-in workspace in the living room, separate bedrooms, front living area could be used for office, workout, or bedroom.  Primary bedroom includes en suite, full bath with a separate vanity area.  Home has large amount of storage, all bedrooms have walk in closets.  Also, has brand new AC unit as of 2022.  Kitchen features granite countertops and breakfast area.  Nice mature trees and covered back patio.  Come tour this charming home in the Brookhollow area. Book your private showing fast.  This home is very close to Austin Elementary and will go super fast!
